&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;由于家居装修零售商 Lowe&amp;#39;s 等&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/hueqwPQmnrw47cA1wF9NhmIBHTBLjfk4y-G5DlKAkRUif6nRVL_aMmiSry2kpK77xu7iZK-bt_Hvywo6WJrW_Z-ce8liKcoDmE586XRvn0iRQT9ZeiOZtdWIljQIG4E-W8L3LfTvwT94MoZ1SSw3gVFoq6cbIntwPbALAlfKS9QOCr2I7_4Ty3LmOmrqo9mqaCtYebjjnsX71uj6r2DxOrlu-RBUk6oN2T2e7B-P-LmC4AZgWShUssQ7-dRXfntNFkL6zCdKysbHgnUILi8X0j2gzM6zMB95xFWG5SOuFbl2dfVhreDLzU-yfLjhY1mtykHNDakvTvZefXR9SKVR6hUQsW4Qn8eh8cVnFRHhHMbR3yz-LTMKACTo_h0/2m3uNKMeUSlrP3qpsvwt-C8HB0razkwB/18" target="_blank"&gt;公司前景黯淡，&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;受美国房地产市场影响的股票&lt;/strong&gt;周三暴跌。投资者还对唐纳德·特朗普总统发表国情咨文演讲期间缺乏住房政策更新做出了反应。标准普尔综合房屋建筑商指数跌幅高达 5.2%，是自去年 4 月“解放日”市场崩溃以来的最大跌幅。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;尽管特朗普昨晚表示两者都不是问题，但两家最大的家居装修连锁店的高管指出， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/EgvwszE0x-laD0JKmh9wa_Z_Fbow54z6bcaZK9KRf_ZdGdJXT2eLk2r8QUtjjkV8d_KWhswuuBZvtvVcGYk5p-hVMS0MK4KEC8AW3iCHR_REMsA8uRzEtTGy87NHSD6kTpmG8cmh8Hr8-E1JscCwA08ZFaaM2yMG0GZsiCvVKFzTSN62PnfhwZ5MwICJikoyhlZItJ6F6PW9P9vMdabuWw4OMuGp7NSa6171Y9ElK4CKK0lNFAnQhBbVzbedMMsmvgtyaaNEXAcAZcnaksuxFITIOyBqXaYYTEzaIhIlul48_dkRj6ZXQ5IuuFVe8jGb2z6BQhZSiqNRH8uCkqCiUOuISDURItysDpP-sa2-g0bkReQPrN-fj2ApWx4/WVKSWPhREhWd7jSDhWgeCIZPhS0vgpFJ/18" target="_blank"&gt;通货膨胀&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/SYfIIm4OjnG2diyWzRb78BEstp7R0omRmTDdHsy_36w2mLypxCtbOWRBj4DXM09V_ipLfIAf-tDZBdsytPrTdsr61ksnJAzRY_as6ZdLO5FMkispZjU9nB3-W7oTfld-AfGu0SmEdC_idzHxDGtHvnd24OJSBeqmPn4kzzsvXwlSDtJSOddx2gwMLOa8xNAhKNfnEpB9kO-RlcxuEiIXnBpaVDQpx2zeskVpWz3PQXoQ-ZUjPbBHpI6h8ZMLKHoEbF1h8yHpdgCAfWxzK_BvAIL4cg-tvtOZausGSd06lBvNdR