t-size: 16px;"&gt;巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦&lt;/strong&gt;和右翼参议员弗拉维奥·博尔索纳罗在 10 月份的总统选举前陷入僵局，该民意调查显示，这场竞选首次出现平局。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;李强总理&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;和德国总理弗里德里希·梅尔茨&lt;/strong&gt;表示，德国领导人抵达北京，这是他去年五月上台以来&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/RF5_p6x3Vk0knoXN8b4gfc92xGXpIFjQBpdJyhisL0RTzWn1naD6md6nuNjj_e-1ZE0CCpuKqvKSz_xb20YtyZtIHROLCWMK28mLNHX5rUIkLLGuA7QxCYSXZVyz71V1n_StyVFr-WjqU39sJFJESTam9XqWc_KmMwegm5q-ujVXn-nZ4XOiptDLDr51VEd4fzoFbX9uLRi4o18OM9g0HgdCZ3d96LtftkIOZ0Y0qf63LE6W2RlUxvNc8G9MvCdRW0_jOSXhBgzfsL_VgvUVYOSCGSx3_yuZJWCDLASLbeSMcwW4HlqIqyvdA1MrpHQOpYKv0OouynbEU6qgG1v1FNF1KvIUhQzC5ASJvhSZhHMDxscgHmvwmCvPZH32P8WfkxUDA9edB671-q7GhObQe4kWq_ch0eUX2jf8kV1opmY7rRz3PKVeHFDB_dGJftdwckKVRh49MPdLtLjjDFVm9H2GKuqgCpdUgmLJXWfwUHTeONdTln53230S_Q3_ngiQEkDShnXqHo4BqBBvqX70/YnV0PTOnvQjIGX6HVmn_7EvVc-MP6Iix/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="中国的李克强和默茨表达了在紧张局势之后改善关系的愿望"&gt;首次对中国进行正式访问&lt;/a&gt;，他们表示希望两国关系得到改善——对贸易和关键矿产供应的担忧将使此次访问变得更加复杂。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/vBZ6RRyBfjGfeAnGe1xuGwIvEFhhZbogLf56MERu6YEnx4a23OMd0e7g8BL4S1QNuGFpVtE2ty1V-G7Q1Lavh3JH9JA4FVsjOet_I_owYiF5kt2KXonmEakZ-5HMBAdyBJRPcpfEm0bnHHY9HQaNRkV2kGKn9XO-oE2mEtrWt409fFFAJe9aXE6sbaU9-sBsI9A1_kraI74vWFl5eVvl4InUboKStKO9ydKAoASY4_jOWzQiUmpe4y1ijJ-4bWdsTNOku3sJGMrn8xGGyjKCxxPeTYk9lntEBdAI4DLyc888q2r2qsHt3dw0O-rD99xVvcfP1an3nphDoM_CXq6MLWGghmFWkdUEFH26ZLnaMNhGNrQ6R-beVKbWbIdKjOzPYv8Tw7PomzWLkvCgPQuXcjJhZ-YhvxuIYiAeIqADpdJHuKuOFdV3mnnTUWG7IgOcK-SnP7uxD274ojEFXIIYZ7IAe3Xq7qTQJ22fptPWm7S0hnEa17iqwkP0QgF42ZUlAmopkdD3BsNqbC79FvaTAA/Fo6VL2n-Jsyztg2WG79L2GC3DcC2e6EU/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="民意调查显示，欧尔班的支持在匈牙利大选前崩溃"&gt;一项新的民意调查&lt;/a&gt;显示，距离议会选举不到七周，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&g